column5: (ID Units:  SF: ) A well-known value 160.  Uniquely identifies this as a SunSpec Multiple MPPT Inverter Extension Model Mode - Range: 160
(L Units:  SF: ) Length of Multiple MPPT Inverter Extension Model - Range: 48
(DCA_SF Units:  SF: ) Current Scale Factor - Range:
(DCV_SF Units:  SF: ) Voltage Scale Factor - Range:
(DCW_SF Units:  SF: ) Power Scale Factor - Range:
(DCWH_SF Units:  SF: ) Energy Scale Factor - Range:
(Evt Units:  SF: ) Global Events - Range:
(N Units:  SF: ) Number of Modules - Range: 2
(TmsPer Units:  SF: ) Timestamp Period - Range: Not supported
(1_ID Units:  SF: ) Input ID - Range: 1
(1_IDStr Units:  SF: ) Input ID Sting - Range: "String 1"
(1_DCA Units: A SF: DCA_SF) DC Current - Range:
(1_DCV Units: V SF: DCV_SF) DC Voltage - Range:
(1_DCW Units: W SF: DCW_SF) DC Power - Range:
(1_DCWH Units: Wh SF: DCWH_SF) Lifetime Energy - Range:
(1_Tms Units: Secs SF: ) Timestamp - Range:
(1_Tmp Units: C SF: ) Temperature - Range:
(1_DCSt Units:  SF: ) Operating State - Range:
(1_DCEvt Units:  SF: ) Module Events - Range:
(2_ID Units:  SF: ) Input ID - Range: 2
(2_IDStr Units:  SF: ) Input ID Sting - Range: "String 2" or "Not supported"
(2_DCA Units: A SF: DCA_SF) DC Current - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_DCV Units: V SF: DCV_SF) DC Voltage - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_DCW Units: W SF: DCW_SF) DC Power - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_DCWH Units: Wh SF: DCWH_SF) Lifetime Energy - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_Tms Units: Secs SF: ) Timestamp - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_Tmp Units: C SF: ) Temperature - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_DCSt Units:  SF: ) Operating State - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
(2_DCEvt Units:  SF: ) Module Events - Range: Not supported if only one DC input.
